messages.content:
Cluster OKE:

```hcl
resource "oci_containerengine_cluster" "oke" {
  compartment_id     = var.compartment_ocid
  kubernetes_version = "v1.28.2"
  name               = "production-oke"
  vcn_id             = oci_core_vcn.main.id
  endpoint_config {
    is_public_ip_enabled = true
    subnet_id            = oci_core_subnet.k8s_endpoint.id
  }
  options {
    service_lb_subnet_ids = [oci_core_subnet.public.id]
    kubernetes_network_config {
      pods_cidr     = "10.244.0.0/16"
      services_cidr = "10.96.0.0/16"
    }
  }
}

resource "oci_containerengine_node_pool" "nodes" {
  compartment_id     = var.compartment_ocid
  cluster_id         = oci_containerengine_cluster.oke.id
  kubernetes_version = "v1.28.2"
  name               = "general-pool"
  node_shape         = "VM.Standard.E4.Flex"
  node_config_details {
    size = 3
    placement_configs {
      availability_domain = "QnsQ:US-ASHBURN-AD-1"
      subnet_id           = oci_core_subnet.k8s_nodes.id
    }
  }
  node_source_details {
    source_type = "IMAGE"
    image_id    = data.oci_containerengine_node_pool_option.oke.sources[0].image_id
  }
  ssh_public_key = file("~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub")
}
```

Doc: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/oracle/oci/latest/docs

Container Instance (serverless containers):

```hcl
resource "oci_container_instances_container_instance" "app" {
  compartment_id       = var.compartment_ocid
  display_name         = "web-app"
  shape                = "CI.Standard.A1.Flex"
  subnet_id            = oci_core_subnet.private.id
  container_restart_policy = "ALWAYS"
  containers {
    display_name = "web-app"
    image_url    = "iad.ocir.io/my-namespace/my-repo:latest"
    resources {
      memory_in_gbs = 4
      ocpus         = 1
    }
    environment_variables = {
      "APP_ENV" = "production"
    }
  }
}
```

**vs OKE:** Container Instance = single container, simples. OKE = Kubernetes, orquestração

Doc: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/oracle/oci/latest/docs

VCN-native networking:

```hcl
resource "oci_containerengine_cluster" "oke" {
  options {
    kubernetes_network_config {
      pods_cidr     = "10.244.0.0/16"
      services_cidr = "10.96.0.0/16"
    }
  }
}

resource "oci_containerengine_node_pool" "pool" {
  node_config_details {
    placement_configs {
      subnet_id = oci_core_subnet.k8s_pods.id  # Subnet dedicada
    }
    node_pool_pod_network_option_details {
      cni_type = "OCI_VCN_IP_NATIVE"
    }
  }
}
```

**Vantagens:** Pods com IPs da VCN, sem overlay, NSGs nos pods

Doc: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/oracle/oci/latest/docs

OCIR:

**1. Auth token:**
```hcl
resource "oci_identity_auth_token" "ocir" {
  description = "OCIR token"
  user_id     = var.user_ocid
}
```

**2. Login:**
```bash
docker login iad.ocir.io
# Username: <namespace>/<username>
# Password: <auth-token>
```

**3. Kubernetes secret:**
```hcl
resource "kubernetes_secret" "ocir" {
  type = "kubernetes.io/dockerconfigjson"
  data = {
    ".dockerconfigjson" = jsonencode({
      auths = {
        "iad.ocir.io" = {
          username = "${var.namespace}/${var.user}"
          password = oci_identity_auth_token.ocir.token
        }
      }
    })
  }
}
```

Doc: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/oracle/oci/latest/docs

Gerenciamento de versões:

**1. Verifique disponíveis:**
```hcl
data "oci_containerengine_cluster_option" "opt" {
  cluster_option_id = "all"
}
output "versions" { value = data.oci_containerengine_cluster_option.opt.kubernetes_versions }
```

**2. Upgrade cluster:**
```hcl
resource "oci_containerengine_cluster" "oke" {
  kubernetes_version = "v1.29.1"  # Nova versão
}
```

**3. Upgrade node pool:** (após cluster)
```hcl
resource "oci_containerengine_node_pool" "nodes" {
  kubernetes_version = "v1.29.1"
}
```

**Best practices:** Teste em staging, verifique compatibilidade de addons, backup etcd

Doc: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/oracle/oci/latest/docs

Add-ons do OKE:

```hcl
resource "oci_containerengine_cluster" "oke" {
  options {
    add_ons {
      is_kubernetes_dashboard_enabled = false
      is_tiller_enabled               = false
    }
    admission_controller_options {
      is_pod_security_policy_enabled = false
    }
    persistent_volume_config {
      freeform_tags = { "Environment" = "production" }
    }
    service_lb_config {
      freeform_tags = { "Environment" = "production" }
    }
  }
}
```

**Add-ons comuns:** Metrics Server (HPA), Cluster Autoscaler, CSI Driver, CNI Plugin

**Deploy via kubectl:** kubectl apply -f metrics-server.yaml

Doc: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/oracle/oci/latest/docs
